Text.Page:
It's good to see the Gutrends put in their place like that. Sooner or later, maybe they'll finally just get out and give us our peace.

Still, though, we're making excellent progress. Crevan at Vindicator Camp will want to know about this.

Since you're responsible for so much of our success, why don't you bring him the message yourself?

You've knocked the Gutrend back several notches, have you? Well, this is wonderful news.

Whimnia will want to hear this as well. Please let her know.

Oh, this is good news.

I'll make a note. I guarantee we'll take advantage of this.
